{"tid":2099063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫潮或煞停泛民初選  參選人意見不一 商討定奪","createTime":"2020-07-08T03:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T03:25:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82749e3a228dfc8cfe67fff551b53711ef203db3","tid":2099063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200708/FE7GQOKZONPNSPFXVC6HDY5L5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FFE7GQOKZONPNSPFXVC6HDY5L5Q%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=68e6ce75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FFE7GQOKZONPNSPFXVC6HDY5L5Q%2F&h=47ba5a1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200708/FE7GQOKZONPNSPFXVC6HDY5L5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n疫潮或煞停泛民初選 <br />\n參選人意見不一 商討定奪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W3kJ7f2Ruf9Pgaxyj1zAJ96CWNY=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TPM6KUNUKBB25Y4ECQGGJXC3VM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW3kJ7f2Ruf9Pgaxyj1zAJ96CWNY%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTPM6KUNUKBB25Y4ECQGGJXC3VM.jpg&h=1cdc0217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴耀廷<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情再現，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n至於是否取消則有不同看法。<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷向本報證實曾經向團隊提出因為疫情肆虐，或需暫停或延遲初選，但最終安排仍未落實，因為不是由他一個人決定，要視乎各區參選人討論結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷憂影響投票意欲<br />\n<br />\n他又指作為協調者有責任提出公共衞生安全問題，亦擔心疫情爆發下市民投票意欲減低，若投票率太低會令選舉沒有認受性，現時要看疫情發展才有最終決定，若幾日後疫情穩定，投票將如常舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8mA_8LZDPF8bmBZcfr60F_Twc1I=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JNMN7WPGWNN4MNLCAK6ECTNIOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8mA_8LZDPF8bmBZcfr60F_Twc1I%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJNMN7WPGWNN4MNLCAK6ECTNIOY.jpg&h=108c4359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武肺疫情再爆發，民主派初選恐押後；圖為2018年立法會補選前，泛民初選投票情況。<br />\n<br />\n參加新界西初選的本土派張可森表示不同意取消初選投票，直言「呢次投票係一個冇DQ情況下，最反映到香港人意願嘅機會，同埋係應對國安法第一個選舉表態，取消嘅話好可惜。」民主黨尹兆堅指若參選人一致認為要取消，願意服從大多數，並指可改行棄選機制，又稱民主派初選距離正式選舉的提名期不足一星期，相信無條件延後，或只能取消選舉。<br />\n<br />\n不過，循新界西爭初選出線權的議會陣線朱凱廸認為，經歷過武肺疫情及北京強推港版國安法，可見香港人面對的困難「從來都係好多」，相信不會因此影響港人在初選投票的決心，甚至不排除「因禍得福」引起更多關注，提高初選投票率。<br />\n<br />\n今次初選約250個票站中，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n顯然是藉着每個當局自製的「稻草人」來令社會停止發聲。"},{"pid":"0580e3730355edaa56c59713cd3c5a6e247f4886","tid":2099063,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fc3f236a0011be53d6e7f215fbd967661a3060","tid":2099063,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"加強番防疫應該ok掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c814a39c9a5ee6dfbd45541ab545bb5e1b0452d5","tid":2099063,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"我都唔想停"},{"pid":"ac59d998980692143de2958e3144fc899d1210f5","tid":2099063,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c814a39c9a5ee6dfbd45541ab545bb5e1b0452d5","tid":2099063,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"我都唔想停"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}